metadata.name: Colorful architecture #1/43
metadata.description:
This series of 43 NFTs combined with AI  were selected from my favorite architecture photos of countries I've been. This collection is unique generative art AI. 
AI art can be of great help, at least for inspiration, for future cities and more colorful world architectures. By non gray cities. I hope you like it.

Artist:  Fabio Cordeiro Negrao
Size: 5000 x 5000 px
